Rapture in Blue ~ Loops 🥀 which is your favorite? 🦈 
While I continue to more properly record Dirty Demos for my upcoming EP, I’ve decided to start releasing the little experimental visuals on YouTube. (Link in bio) As I journey into the creative digital abyss, I shall fear no imperfections~ visually or vocally. Experimentation is my favorite way to learn 🧪

Experimenting with hand coloring 🤖🎨 I wanted to play with some colors that felt poppy 🍒I’m gonna try some different colorings & process, but wanted to share some simple experiments with you along the way. 🌙

How Strange, Dirty Demo 🌀
Filmed Live.. 
While struggling with shyness, knowing Brooklyn roommates were an ear shot away… But that’s what I think makes this demo a little extra special… I can hear the pain in this song, burning inside my chest, finding its way out against its stage fright.. I needed to purge this tune from within me, & I did. 🧨
Performed live, then added harmonies in post. 
🥀I’ve gone into more detail about this tune on my Patreon, And I’ve added this to my YouTube channel as I continue to purge all Dirty Demos, creating space for more art :) Feel free to give my YouTube channel some love 🥀✨ as I’m continuing to build it, brick by 🧱 (link in bio) ✨ Wishing you a beautiful inspired day xoxo

Alright it’s time….
Betty-Who, Returns 
🍭❄️🍦❄️🍭 
Three Peppermint twists,
And a kiss on the lips,
She twisted & lifted 
And thought about “the list”…
“But what if nice was naughty, and naughty was nice? 
Oh what a world it would be!” 
Betty-who dreamt that Christmas night.🍦

🌑 I spent a little time putting some giffs onto Spotify for the album Silver Planet with the brilliant @chris_hunt_0 mastered mastered by @doctormillice recorded at @bunkerstudio 🔥 I had to share this snippet of music video from our song Tosca, as I just love @chris_hunt_0 ‘s surreal camera & edit visions 🌑✨ I’m glad we got to make this Ep together Chris!
And if you wanna see the little Giffs, you can view on Spotify from a mobile device :) Silver Planet 🪐 Kacie Marie & Chris Hunt ⚔️ & if you wanna see and hear the music videos, they’re on my YouTube 📺 YouTube.com/KacieMarieOnMars

The last of the seasons snow 💙🧊 & What better way to ode to its Blue Beauty, than sharing a tiny snippet of the Brilliant & Dynamic album by @the.no.ring.circus @mr.eli.rose ⚔️ That is Now Streaming Everywhere 📻 & Yes, I did share the small piece of song where I sang a little Ooo’s & Ahhh’s, but my little vocals are mere morsels in the Feast of this album. I was honored to be a little bird singing in the back, & I hope that You enjoy this record as much as I do ✨🪐

As spring slowly approaches, I feel it’s glow beckoning me from the shadows.. I await with patience for its fragrance and glory… Daydreaming of buds blooming and birds singing. With growth from the ground and all around 🌱✨
The Spring, it beckons me.
———
May you find some peace in today, tomorrow, and the next to come. I know that it’s hard times for so many people in so many different ways. May the sun warm your cheeks & brighten your soul, through the dark times. ☀️🍀
With Love,
Kacie

These are too cool not to post 🍎✨ this gorgeous mural wall is still standing strong, and I am forever honored that @nonperishable painted me upon these bricks. As a kid growing up in Pa, when sitting in the backseat driving into the city to see the Phillies play, I would always ogle all of the murals along the way.. Daydreaming of painting murals in my adult life. Never did I dream that I’d get to be part of the mural itself🌈 Thank you for that @nonperishable ✨
